languages.text: "Без девчонки?.. Что ж, по крайней мере, мы живы. Благодарю вас, Вольный Торговец. Дом Орселлио на забудет вашей мудрости и доброты".

languages.text: “不能带那姑娘一起走吗？我猜，我们捡了条命，已经够意思了。谢谢您，行商浪人，奥赛罗家族永远不会忘记您的智慧与慷慨。”
languages.original_text: "Without the girl? I guess we are alive, which is something. Thank you, Rogue Trader. House Orsellio will not forget your wisdom and generosity."

traits.locale_text: “不能带那姑娘一起走吗？我猜，我们捡了条命，已经够意思了。谢谢您，行商浪人，奥塞罗家族永远不会忘记您的智慧与慷慨。”
traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: «¿Sin la chica? Bueno, supongo que seguir vivos ya es bastante. Gracias, Comerciante Independiente. La casa Orsellio no olvidará su sabiduría y generosidad».
languages.original_text: "Without the girl? I guess we are alive, which is something. Thank you, Rogue Trader. House Orsellio will not forget your wisdom and generosity."

languages.text: 「あの少女抜きで？我々はどういうわけか生きている。感謝するわ、自由開拓者。オーセリオ家は、あなたの知恵と寛大さを忘れることはないでしょう」
languages.original_text: "Without the girl? I guess we are alive, which is something. Thank you, Rogue Trader. House Orsellio will not forget your wisdom and generosity."

traits.locale_text: 「あの少女抜きで？我々はどういうわけか生きている。感謝するわ、自由開拓者。オーセリオ家は、あなたの知恵と寛大さを忘れることはないでしょう」
traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: "Ohne das Mädchen? Na ja, immerhin sind wir am Leben. Danke, {mf|Freihändler|Freihändlerin}. Das Haus Orsellio wird Eure Weisheit und Großzügigkeit nicht vergessen."
languages.original_text: "Without the girl? I guess we are alive, which is something. Thank you, Rogue Trader. House Orsellio will not forget your wisdom and generosity."

languages.text: « Sans l'enfant ? J'imagine que nous devrions déjà nous réjouir d'être en vie. Merci, {mf|libre-marchand|libre-marchande}. La maison Orsellio saura se souvenir de votre sagesse et de votre générosité. »
languages.original_text: "Without the girl? I guess we are alive, which is something. Thank you, Rogue Trader. House Orsellio will not forget your wisdom and generosity."

languages.text: "Kız olmadan mı? En azından canımızdan olmadık, bu da bir şey. Teşekkürler Hür Tacir. Orsellio Hanesi, akil yaklaşımınızı ve cömertliğinizi unutmayacak."
